Odaily Planet Daily News According to the monitoring of Ai Yi, an analyst on the chain, during the pre-sale fundraising stage of Meme coin PAIN, the whale "5r2kw...Aq1Bv" invested 20,000 SOL (worth $4.3 million at the time) to become the TOP1 payment address, accounting for 10.74% of the total fund pool.
In addition, according to the pre-sale payment situation, after the airdrop is distributed in proportion, the distribution of the front-row chips is as follows:
TOP5: 32,747 SOL, holding a total of 17.6%;
TOP10: 43,242 SOL, holding a total of 23.2%;
TOP20: 59,299 SOL, holding a total of 31.87%
The total proportion of TOP20 holdings exceeds one-third. If they are sold after the opening, it may have a great impact on the price of the currency.
